e Ages."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Peter Fawconberg was born about 1125. He had at least 2 sons and 1 daughter with Beatrice."},"et":{"about 1125 –":"umbes 1125–Surnud","1130–Female":"1130–Surnud","1150–1226":"1150–1226","1152–Female":"1152–Surnud","1159–Male":"1159–Surnud","1125–Male":"1125–Surnud","Abt 1152":"umbes 1152","1226":"1226","1159":"1159","1125":"1125","abt. 1159":"umbes 1159","about 1125 ":"umbes 1125","1152":"1152","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","Rise, Holderness, East Riding, Yorkshire, England":"Rise, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Rise in Holderness, Yorkshire, England":"Rise, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1125 –":"noin 1125–Kuollut","1130–Female":"1130–Kuollut","1150–1226":"1150–1226","1152–Female":"1152–Kuollut","1159–Male":"1159–Kuollut","1125–Male":"1125–Kuollut","Abt 1152":"noin 1152","1226":"1226","1159":"1159","1125":"1125","abt. 1159":"noin 1159","about 1125 ":"noin 1125","1152":"1152","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire, England","Rise, Holderness, East Riding, Yorkshire, England":"Rise, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Rise in Holderness, Yorkshire, England":"Rise, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1125 –":"environ 1125–Décédé","1130–Female":"1130–Décédée","1150–1226":"1150–1226","1152–Female":"1152–Décédée","1159–Male":"1159–Décédé","1125–Male":"1125–Décédé","Abt 1152":"environ 1152","1226":"1226","1159":"1159","1125":"1125","abt. 1159":"environ 1159","about 1125 ":"environ 1125","1152":"1152","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","Yorkshire, England":"Everwyck, Angleterre","Rise, Holderness, East Riding, Yorkshire, England":"Rise, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Rise in Holderness, Yorkshire, England":"Rise, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Peter Fawconberg est né environ 1125. Il a eu au moins 2 fils et 1 fille avec Beatrice."},"de":{"about 1125 –":"um 1125–Verstorben","1130–Female":"113